data.description: Seller offering $25k credit. Your piece of paradise awaits you! 2188sf home sits on all usable 5.170 acres. HUGE Shop 32X64, 3 bays (2)10 ft doors & 12ft door insulated w/220, loft area, office, tool rm & wood stove. 3 bdrms 2 bath home. 4bed Septic. Enter thru living rm w/wood stove & lg windows, letting PNW sun in. Kitchen w/breakfast bar, separate family rm, 3 spacious bdrms Primary has walk-in closet & full bath. Garage finished as Bonus rm. Covered back porch. Garden area, fenced back yd. 2greenhouses, fruit trees, sheds, well house w/new well pump, Water is best around. RV bay w/outlet, carport, Barn w/stalls.2 chicken coops. Stream at back of property large trout caught. Mins to Mineral lake, mins to Mt. Rainier & Skiing White pass.
